# Database Schema & Convex Integration

## Core Database Tables (convex/schema.ts)

### Users Table
```typescript
{
  _id: string,
  email: string,
  firstName: string,
  lastName: string,
  phone?: string,
  passwordHash?: string, // Optional for Facebook users
  role: "client" | "admin" | "super_admin",
  isActive?: boolean,
  // Facebook integration
  facebookId?: string,
  profilePicture?: string,
  loginMethod?: "email" | "facebook",
  createdAt: number,
  updatedAt: number
}
```

### Products Table
```typescript
{
  _id: string,
  name: string,
  description?: string,
  price: number,
  originalPrice?: number,
  categoryId: string,
  image: string,
  images?: string[],
  certificate?: string,
  sku?: string | number,
  stock: number,
  rating?: number,
  reviews?: number,
  badge?: string,
  productStatus?: string,
  lifespan?: string,
  isActive: boolean,
  createdAt: number,
  updatedAt: number
}
```

### Specialized Product Data
- **Fish Data:** Scientific name, size, temperature, pH, origin, diet
- **Tank Data:** Type, material, capacity, dimensions, thickness, lighting

### Orders & Reservations
- **Orders:** Full e-commerce orders with shipping and payment tracking
- **Reservations:** Multi-item reservation system for live fish with pickup scheduling
- **Cart:** Supports both authenticated users and guests

## Convex Services Structure
- [convex/services/auth.ts](mdc:convex/services/auth.ts) - User authentication and management
- [convex/services/products.ts](mdc:convex/services/products.ts) - Product catalog operations
- [convex/services/orders.ts](mdc:convex/services/orders.ts) - Order processing
- [convex/services/reservations.ts](mdc:convex/services/reservations.ts) - Reservation management
- [convex/services/cart.ts](mdc:convex/services/cart.ts) - Shopping cart operations
- [convex/services/notifications.ts](mdc:convex/services/notifications.ts) - Notification system
- [convex/services/admin.ts](mdc:convex/services/admin.ts) - Admin operations

## TypeScript Types
All database types are defined in [types/index.ts](mdc:types/index.ts) with strict TypeScript interfaces.

## Important Patterns
- Use Convex reactive queries for real-time data
- Support both user and guest data access patterns
- Maintain backward compatibility with legacy single-item reservations
- Use proper indexing for query performance